start: (hexdigits|digits|alphanumerics|letters|start) /:\/\// (alphanumerics|whitespaces|letters|hexdigits|digits|start) /\?/ (whitespaces|alphanumerics|letters|hexdigits|printables|digits|start) | /http:\/\// (alphanumerics|whitespaces|letters|hexdigits|digits|start) | (hexdigits|digits|alphanumerics|letters|start) /:\/\// (alphanumerics|whitespaces|letters|hexdigits|digits|start) | /http:\/\// (whitespaces|alphanumerics|letters|hexdigits|digits|start) /\?/ (whitespaces|alphanumerics|letters|hexdigits|printables|digits|start) | /:/ (alphanumerics|whitespaces|letters|hexdigits|digits|start) | (whitespaces|alphanumerics|letters|hexdigits|digits|start) /:/ (alphanumerics|whitespaces|letters|hexdigits|digits|start) | (alphanumerics|whitespaces|letters|hexdigits|digits|start) | (alphanumerics|whitespaces|letters|hexdigits|printables|digits|start) /\#/ (digits|letters|whitespaces|punctuations|alphanumerics|hexdigits|printables|start) | /http:/ (alphanumerics|whitespaces|letters|hexdigits|digits|start) | /http:/ (alphanumerics|whitespaces|letters|hexdigits|printables|digits|start) /\#/ (digits|letters|whitespaces|punctuations|alphanumerics|hexdigits|printables|start)
printables: (LETTER | INT | WS | /[!"#$%&'()*+,-.\/:;<=>?@[\\]^_`{|}~]/)+

whitespaces: WS
letters: LETTER
punctuations: /[!"#$%&'()*+,-.\/:;<=>?@[\\]^_`{|}~]/
hexdigits: HEXDIGIT+
digits: INT
